Hi {0}
We are so excited to have you onboard and looking forward to assisting you every step of the way. OneHub is a Standard Bank Corporate and Investment Banking platform that holds all the digital solutions and offerings into a single place for ease of use with a single sign-on to gain access to all information, solutions and offerings.
Enjoy and let us know if we can assist you in anyway.
Regards, OneHub team
The above tabs will allow you to access different sections of OneHub. Take some time to explore the sections. Will be worth your while.

Access all Solutions that are tailored for you and the work you need to perform. All signed-up Solutions will appear as their own tile on your dashboard.

If you have a thought about any of the Solutions, you can share it in our MarketPlace community.

View all API Products and access the swagger documentation or subscribe to an API Product.

If you have an opinion or point of view in regards to any of our API Products, you can add your thoughts in our MarketPlace community.

Get the latest insights in relation to your industry. Here you can watch and read or view all available insights that have been provided just for you from Standard Bank industry experts. Happy reading.
You can interact with Stan the helpful service bot who will assist the best way he can to solve any of your issues or concerns. All good?

Okay, now that you have an idea of OneHub and what you can do, you can invite team members.

If you don't want to invite team members right now, no problem, you can always use the "Team Profile" section under the dashboard main menu.

Okay, now that you have an idea of OneHub and what you can do. You can invite others.

If you don't want to invite others right now, no problem, you can always use the "Team profile" section under the main menu.
Here you can do many things that will enhance your day to day. Let's have a look around. Ready to get started?
Here you are able to do a couple of things that we would like to take the time to explain to you.

Here you can invite team members to join you in OneHub. As an authorised person, you can toggle who is able to send further invites to their respective teams. You are responsible for managing the access of every person you invite.
Here you can invite your team members to join you in OneHub. You are responsible for managing the access of every person you invite.
Here you can manage previously sent invites to remind team members that have not yet signed up to sign up. Once they have signed up, you can either Decline or Approve their access.

Once you approve a team members access in the Pending approval section, they will then move to your Team details. Here you can manage their access. If you deactivate a team member, they are not able to access OneHub nor any of the solutions they are signed up for.
Great! Now that you know what you can do, you can go ahead and start inviting team members to access OneHub. If you need anything, let us know using our Contact us section.
